To compile firewire program do as following:
1. verify the path to EPICS 3.14[.7] in ../../setup.sh
2. source the ../../setup.sh
   example:	
   . ../../setup.sh
3. make -f MakefileApp

To start the firewire application do es following:

1. Set correctly LD_LIBRARY_PATH variable to point o epics 3.14[.7]
  example:	
	export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=~dach/EPICS3.14.7/base-3.14.7/lib/linux-x86/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
2. start the client application by typing:
   firewire.sh <EPICS camera device name>
